title: "One Logic — Many UI"
description: "Run everywhere: CLI, Web, and Native."
icon: "layers"
order: 2
metrics:
  platforms: 3
  logic_reuse: "100%"
content: |
  # Polymorphic UI
  The core `EditorModel` is completely isolated from the presentation layer. 
  
  This allows us to run the SAME business logic in:
  - **Terminal (CLI)** for power users and CI pipelines.
  - **Browser (Web)** for collaboration and visual editing.
  - **Native Apps** for mobile and offline access.
